-- China Will Spend `Hundreds of Billions' Repairing Reservoirs, Xinhua Says
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-12T15:46:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/china-will-spend-hundreds-of-billions-repairing-reservoirs-xinhua-says.html
China will invest “hundreds of
billions of yuan” to repair dilapidated small- and medium-sized
reservoirs over the next five years, Xinhua News Agency said,
citing Du Ying, deputy director of the National Development annd
Reform Commission, the nation’s top planning body.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
